Add a Scaling Layer

Notes:

library(gridExtra)
library(ggplot2)
p1 <- ggplot(aes(x = friend_count), data = pf) +
  geom_histogram() 

p2 <- p1 + scale_x_log10()

p3 <- p1 + scale_x_sqrt()

grid.arrange(p1, p2, p3, ncol = 1)
